# -*-cperl-*-

=head1 NAME

CALC_SCUBA2_NEFD - Recipe for calculating NEFDs from SCUBA-2 images

=head1 DESCRIPTION

A simple PICARD recipe to calculate the NEFD from reduced SCUBA-2
images.

=head1 NOTES

The input data are calibrated if necessary.

The results of the calculation are printed to the screen and written
to a log file, C<log.nefd>.

=head1 DISPLAY

No display is used by this recipe.

